{"tid":2346338,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(live) 下午左右民眾已經紛紛上山追雪","createTime":"2020-12-30T07:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T07:42:24.000Z","uid":253829,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"97e5a85614fcd7f1925638e272926d8b901de7b2","tid":2346338,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"陽明山國家公園的多支監視器鏡頭顯示，到處都是下雨起大霧，有時還可感覺得強大陣風，吹的樹枝不斷搖曳，至下午左右，已有追雪人潮上山，甚至可以看到年輕人騎機車揪團上山，展現年輕人活力十足的一面。<br />\n<br />\n民間氣象公司「天氣風險WeatherRisk」在粉專提醒，白天持續降溫，今晚、明晨將是寒流最冷的時間，北部與宜蘭下探7℃、中部8℃、南部9-12℃、花東9-11℃。另外降雪機率很高，「天氣風險」指出，陽明山的大屯山、桃園拉拉山、宜蘭太平山氣溫已近冰點，「預估中午前後有機會開始降雪，持續至今天晚間。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.live/yms/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.live%2Fyms%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSEwAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=4ca41628\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.live/yms/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GFqsREyBIf0&amp;feature=emb_title&amp;ab_channel=%E9%99%BD%E6%98%8E%E5%B1%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGFqsREyBIf0%26feature%3Demb_title%26ab_channel%3D%25E9%2599%25BD%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSEwAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=57819a7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GFqsREyBIf0&amp;feature=emb_title&amp;ab_channel=%E9%99%BD%E6%98%8E%E5%B1%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iot2IHfilic&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIot2IHfilic%26feature%3Demb_title&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSEwAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=53833f48\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iot2IHfilic&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xqrxucoKeME&amp;feature=emb_title&amp;ab_channel=%E9%99%BD%E6%98%8E